Introduction

Jeong JinSoul is a South Korean singer-songwriter and rapper under MODHAUS. She is a member of the girl group ARTMS, and its sub-unit ODD EYE CIRCLE. She is also a former member of the girl group LOONA.

According to the LOONAverse, she lives in the Middle Earth along with Kim Lip and Choerry.

She was featured on ViVi's "Everyday I Need You" ahead of her official reveal on June 13th, 2017 where she was revealed as a member and subsequently released her solo single album "JinSoul" on June 26th, 2017

JinSoul debuted as a member of LOONA on August 20, 2018, with their first mini album "[+ +]".

On May 31, 2024, Jinsoul debuted as a member of ARTMS with their first album "Dall".
